<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 03:29:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示中国房价在放缓后预计到2026年将趋于稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-home-prices-set-stabilise-by-2026-after-slower-falls-2024-11-29/</link><description>路透调查显示，随着一系列扭转多年房地产低迷的支持措施开始取得成效，预计今明两年中国房价下跌速度将放缓，并在 2026 年趋于稳定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 02:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-home-prices-set-stabilise-by-2026-after-slower-falls-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>家人称，中国法院以间谍罪判处记者董宇宇7年有期徒刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-court-sentences-journalist-dong-yuyu-7-years-spy-charges-family-says-2024-11-29/</link><description>一名家人告诉路透社，北京一家法院周五以间谍罪判处中国官方媒体资深记者董玉玉七年有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 02:46:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-court-sentences-journalist-dong-yuyu-7-years-spy-charges-family-says-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市下滑，日本央行加息押注日元创 4 个月来最佳单周表现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-29/</link><description>亚洲股市周五下跌，而日元有望创四个月来最佳单周表现，因为强劲的当地通胀数据让交易员倾向于日本央行即将加息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国11月份制造业活动连续第二个月扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-nov-manufacturing-activity-seen-expanding-second-month-2024-11-29/</link><description>11月份中国工厂活动可能连续第二个月小幅扩张，近期一系列数据表明一系列刺激措施终于开始实施，并为世界第二大经济体的生产商带来急需的提振。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-nov-manufacturing-activity-seen-expanding-second-month-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示大型钢铁制造商未能转向可再生能源</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/big-steelmakers-failing-make-switch-renewables-survey-shows-2024-11-29/</link><description>周五对 18 家领先企业的调查显示，全球最大的钢铁制造商在向低碳生产转型方面落后了，其中一些钢铁制造商的能源仍然完全依赖化石燃料。</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 00:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/big-steelmakers-failing-make-switch-renewables-survey-shows-2024-11-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国法院将宣判资深记者间谍案 - 媒体集团</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-court-announce-verdict-veteran-journalist-spy-case-media-group-2024-11-28/</link><description>据一家倡导释放的美国记者组织称，北京一家法院预计将于周五对一名中国官方媒体资深记者一案作出判决，该记者在 2022 年与一名日本外交官会面后因间谍罪被拘留。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 23:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-court-announce-verdict-veteran-journalist-spy-case-media-group-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构报告称伊朗计划新的铀浓缩扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-plans-uranium-enrichment-expansion-natanz-fordow-iaea-report-says-2024-11-28/</link><description>更大的浓缩能力可能会增加核扩散风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 19:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-plans-uranium-enrichment-expansion-natanz-fordow-iaea-report-says-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示希望特朗普重新考虑对墨西哥和加拿大征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/biden-says-he-hopes-trump-rethinks-tariffs-mexico-canada-2024-11-28/</link><description>拜登表示，征收关税可能会“破坏”与亲密盟友的关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 16:35:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/biden-says-he-hopes-trump-rethinks-tariffs-mexico-canada-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>法国、德国、瑞典敦促欧盟推动电池行业避免对中国的依赖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/france-germany-sweden-urge-eu-battery-sector-push-avoid-china-reliance-2024-11-28/</link><description>法国、德国和瑞典周四呼吁即将上任的欧盟委员会确保欧洲电池生产的未来，并避免依赖中国来满足其绿色转型的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:36:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/france-germany-sweden-urge-eu-battery-sector-push-avoid-china-reliance-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>瑞典要求中国配合波罗的海电缆调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-china-cooperate-baltic-sea-cable-investigation-2024-11-28/</link><description>瑞典首相乌尔夫·克里斯特森周四表示，瑞典已向中国发出正式请求，寻求合作，帮助澄清波罗的海两条海底电缆受损的情况。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/sweden-asks-china-cooperate-baltic-sea-cable-investigation-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大清算人向其子公司提交清盘申请</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/liquidators-china-evergrande-file-winding-up-petition-against-cos-unit-2024-11-28/</link><description>房地产开发商中国恒大的清算人周四向天脊控股提交了一份清盘申请，该公司是风景之旅发行的某些境外优先票据的担保人，风景之旅也是该集团的成员。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 14:21:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/liquidators-china-evergrande-file-winding-up-petition-against-cos-unit-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卫星图像显示中国船只聚集在与菲律宾有争议的岛屿附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ships-gather-near-island-disputed-with-philippines-satellite-images-show-2024-11-28/</link><description>在线船舶追踪器显示，卫星照片中的许多船只都是中国注册的渔船。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 11:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-ships-gather-near-island-disputed-with-philippines-satellite-images-show-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普执政一个月后，世界市场面临现实检验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-graphic-graphic-2024-11-28/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 于 11 月 5 日赢得美国大选，11 月是赢家和输家明显的一个月。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 10:32:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-graphic-graphic-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>如果美国升级芯片限制，中国警告将采取“必要行动”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-warns-necessary-actions-if-us-escalates-chip-curbs-2024-11-28/</link><description>有报道称拜登政府最早可能在本周公布新的出口限制措施，中国周四警告称，如果美国升级芯片控制措施，中国将采取“必要行动”保护中国企业。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 10:16:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-warns-necessary-actions-if-us-escalates-chip-curbs-2024-11-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，财团计划在未来几周内完成 ESR 收购，估值可能超过 70 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/consortium-aims-seal-esr-buyout-coming-weeks-likely-valuing-it-over-7-bln-say-2024-11-28/</link><description>两位消息人士称，包括喜达屋资本集团和华平投资集团在内的财团计划在未来几周内敲定将 ESR 集团私有化的交易，这家在香港上市的房地产基金管理公司的估值将超过 70 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 09:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/consortium-aims-seal-esr-buyout-coming-weeks-likely-valuing-it-over-7-bln-say-2024-11-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>